#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_directory.rst:156
msgid ""
"On Windows, returns the name of the drive (partition) passed as an "
"argument (e.g. ``C:``). On other platforms, or if the requested drive "
"does not existed, the method returns an empty String."
